food, rice,
lentils, and other supplies, all
desperately

02:07.561 --> 02:10.130 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
needed.

02:10.163 --> 02:15.769 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
