34:56.528 --> 35:01.599 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
been kidnapped and killed in
Mexico for covering
organized crime and official
corruption, which

35:01.633 --> 35:07.238 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
often intersects. So, this is
really a very
troubling thing, treated as kind
of an entertainment-style

35:07.272 --> 35:11.743 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
news story, when we have people
dying, journalists
in Mexico risking their lives to
bring their

35:11.776 --> 35:13.545 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
readers and viewers the truth.

35:13.578 --> 35:18.249 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: So, do you
think the public
is served in any way by Sean
Penn's -- quote,

