have a Hollywood

35:45.443 --> 35:51.516 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
actor and a Mexican soap opera
star who plays
a queenpin, a drug queenpin, in
a soap opera

35:51.549 --> 35:56.588 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
in Mexico finding their way into
this jungle
hideaway, at the invitation of
Mexico's most

35:56.621 --> 35:58.390 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
wanted man.

35:58.423 --> 36:02.293 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
That story, how they were able
to get there
-- and there are photos on --
from Mexican

36:02.327 --> 36:06.331 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
paparazzi that actually show the
