37:38.056 --> 37:42.127 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, what Sean Penn did probably
is not new
for Mexican journalists, but he
obviously

37:42.160 --> 37:44.095 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
faced none of the risks that
they face every
day.

37:44.129 --> 37:47.232 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: All right, and
just for
the record, we did reach out to
"Rolling Stone,"

37:47.265 --> 37:49.033 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
