48:20.898 --> 48:24.034 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ROGER BONAIR-AGARD, The Poetry
Foundation:
As you might imagine, the young
people here

48:24.068 --> 48:29.106 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
