back because of that.

49:19.990 --> 49:24.161 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But, really, if people sit down
and get to
know me, like, such as yourself,
you will

49:24.195 --> 49:29.967 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
know and learn that I'm a good
person, I'm
a good kid, and I'm not what
they think I

49:30.000 --> 49:32.503 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
am. I'm much better than what
