49:32.536 --> 49:34.705 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
RYAN KEESLING, Director, Free
Write Jail Arts
and Literacy: Our work is
grounded in narrative.

49:34.738 --> 49:38.275 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Ryan Keesling is
the director
of Free Write.

49:38.309 --> 49:44.348 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
RYAN KEESLING: Those issues are
their personal
issues that are serious, and
they need to

49:44.381 --> 49:48.452 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
be processed in some way. Like,
we're not
coming and saying, oh, you did
this, or you

49:48.485 --> 49:51.222 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
