you, you
had this happen to you,
therefore, you are

49:51.255 --> 49:52.957 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
this kind of person.

49:52.990 --> 49:57.695 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And we just allow those issues
to sort of
come to the surface, and
assemble pieces of

49:57.728 --> 50:00.931 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
