experiences.

50:00.965 --> 50:05.269 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
STUDENT: So, let me grab the
broken pieces,
and use my thoughts as glue, put
it all back

50:05.302 --> 50:09.607 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
