you how this works. He handed me
a handful

50:16.647 --> 50:20.284 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
of crack and put a .22 on my
waistline, which
was hidden behind my shirt. He
said, there's

50:20.317 --> 50:23.520 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
money to be made, and you will
find out what
it's worth, setting me up to die
early, which

50:23.554 --> 50:25.322 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
say he ain't care about my
birth.

50:25.356 --> 50:29.627 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: In a place like
this, does
writing get you respect? It is
something you

50:29.660 --> 50:31.695 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
-- that everybody knows you do,
or...

50:31.729 --> 50:34.498 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
STUDENT: It's definitely
something everybody
know I do.

50:34.531 --> 50:40.070 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
To me, like, they look at it as
