51:43.734 --> 51:45.169 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
LEONARD DIXON, Superintendent,
Cook County
Juvenile Temporary Detention
Center: Detention

51:45.202 --> 51:48.138 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
