52:08.926 --> 52:11.729 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
JEFFREY BROWN: Yes. This
facility is predominantly
African-American.

52:11.762 --> 52:12.930 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
LEONARD DIXON: Yes, it's...

52:12.963 --> 52:14.765 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Far higher
